Amazon logo, search by XPATH, (By.XPATH, //*[@class='a-icon a-icon-logo']")
Continue button, search by id, (By.ID, 'continue')
Need help link, search by XPATH, (By.XPATH, "//a[text()='Need help']")
Forgot your password link, search by XPATH, (By.XPATH, "//a[contains(@href, 'forgotpassword')]")
Other issues with Sign-In link, search by id, (By.ID, 'ap-other-signin-issues-link')
Create your Amazon account button, search by id, (By.ID, 'createAccountSubmit')
Conditions of use link, search by XPATH, (By.XPATH, "//a[text()='Conditions of Use']")
Privacy Notice link, search by XPATH, (By.XPATH, "//a[contains(@href, 'privacy_notice')]")